(35, 'F1 Solutions', '<img src="/uploads/12-06-05/F1-logo.jpg" alt="" /><br /><p><strong>F1 Solutions Sdn Bhd</strong>, a wireless turnkey distribution company has its strong focus and presence within APAC particularly in Malaysia, Indonesia, Philippines and China aim to provide complete end-to-end wireless solution for its business partners and customers. Our wireless solutions cover the access, distribution and core layers of traditional TDM to IP Ethernet from Point-to-multipoint and Point-to-point radios in Sub 6Ghz and 7Ghz to 24Ghz.</p><p>  As a complete package, we offer to consult, built, operate and transfer services including distributed and centralized wireless infrastructure and service management platform for Government, Enterprise, Service Providers and Carriers. This includes automation of service provisioning, customers’ relationship management, billing and control irrespective of the sizes of subscribers’ base.</p><br /> Email:   <a href="mailto:jt@f1.net.my">jt@f1.net.my</a>         <br />Contact: Mr. Jim Teo       <br />              Mobile: +6012-2102717  <br />  <br />  <a href="http://www.f1dotcom.my" target="_blank">www.f1dotcom.my</a>', '', 0, '2012-06-05 22:30:35', '2012-06-05 22:31:05'),
