(105, 'Steakwave', '<img src="/uploads/12-06-05/streakwave.jpg" alt="" /><h2>Distributor in USA and Canada</h2><p>Streakwave Wireless Inc, is a Global Value Added Distributor with distribution facilities in San Jose California and Salt Lake City Utah and is proud to offer a complete line of wireless solutions from top tier manufacturers. Streakwave offers equipment which utilizes both licensed and licensed free bands available for public use. Solutions include; Point to Point back hauls, Point to Multipoint systems and equipment for all other types of wireless and wired network applications. Primarily, Streakwave serves the Educational, Government, Corporate, Healthcare, Security and Consumer markets.</p><p>Streakwave prides itself on technical knowledge of the industry offering first tier technical support for most every product offered. Streakwave Wireless’ Sales Engineering / Account Management Team verbally assists our customers with all aspects of design, layout of networks, trouble shooting, site survey assistance and implementation. These attributes accompanied by unparalleled customer service proves Streakwave Wireless, Inc. is the leader among product equipment providers. Streakwave Wireless believes in outstanding customer service and we have built a quality team that will exceed the needs of our customers.</p><br /><a href="http://www.streakwave.com" target="_blank">www.streakwave.com</a>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:21:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(106, 'DoubleRadius', '<img src="/uploads/12-06-05/dradius.gif" alt="" /><h2>Distributor in USA and Canada</h2><p>DoubleRadius, Inc. was formed for the sole purpose of providing best of breed networking, consulting, designing, planning and financing solutions to the data communications community. We are focused on a wide range of customers including WISPs, municipalities, service providers, telecommunications companies, and utility companies.</p><p>Our full spectrum of resources combines a complete range of innovative products with the most experienced, knowledgeable professionals in the industry. We have partnered with the best manufacturers in the world to concentrate on WAN & LAN connectivity requirements including wireless, dial-up, DSL, routing, and switching.</p><p>Our solutions-oriented approach is driven by our desire to exceed the expectations of our customers.</p><br /><a href="http://www.doubleradius.com" target="_blank">www.doubleradius.com</a>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:21:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(107, 'Crossover ', '<img src="/uploads/12-06-05/crossover_logo_col_197_35.jpg" alt="" /><h2>Distributor in USA and Canada</h2><p>Crossover distribution Corp is a value-added distributor of wireless broadband, in-building cellular, telecom, VoIP, data networking and CATV technologies to the North American marketplace.  These technologies are purchased by telephone companies, internet service providers, cable TV operators and a national network of integrators, certified dealers, value-added resellers and contractors.They provide full service sales, engineering, technical support and logistics for their key vendor partners.  Crossover has a breakthrough, secure, password protected E-Commerce website that resellers can use to place and track orders, as well as review ordering history and pricing rates.  With Canadian offices located in Torontoand a US office located in Parsippany, New Jersey, they offer North American coverage and smooth order fulfillment.</p><br /><a href="http://www.crossoverdistribution.com/" target="_blank">www.crossoverdistribution.com/</a>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:21:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
