(142, 'About us', '        <p>        LigoWave was founded in 2007 as a manufacturer and developer of high performance, versatile <strong>wireless solutions</strong> for Wireless Internet Service Providers and Telecoms across the globe. Making use of industry-leading wireless technology, LigoWave products are developed with the carrier-grade customer in mind. By utilizing cutting edge hardware platforms as well as robust software technology to handle the security and management needs of today’s growing wireless infrastructure, LigoWave products deliver a customized <strong>wireless solution</strong> with performance and stability that is unparalleled in the wireless market today.        </p>        <br /><br />        <p>        LigoWave broadband access solutions operate in licensed and unlicensed frequency bands and are divided into <strong><a href="#" class="red">point-to-point</a></strong> (LigoPTP) and mesh (LigoMESH) product lines.  All LigoWave products use a proprietary protocol which ensures robustness and exceptional performance. Years of experience in the wireless industry and feedback from our customers, partners and colleagues allows us to develop a carrier-grade product line with exclusive features not seen elsewhere in the market today.        </p>        <br /><br />        <p>        Along with our high-quality products, we offer exceptional guidance and support for our customers scattered throughout  150 countries around the world.  Our customer base ranges from Telecom operators to smaller wireless internet service providers, system integrators and wireless equipment distributors.        </p>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:21:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(143, 'Mission and vision', '                <h2>Our mission</h2>                <p>                We are committed to quality, innovation and performance and these values remain core during the development, production and distribution processes of LigoWave <strong><a href="#" class="red">wireless</a></strong> equipment. Today’s rapidly changing and quickly evolving <strong>wireless</strong> communication market requires swift reaction to the changes, dedication to quality and cost-effectiveness to deliver the desirable solutions to customers. LigoWave will continue to develop and produce premier line carrier grade <strong>wireless</strong> networking products and market them through its worldwide distribution network using the core values of the company.                </p>                <h2>Our vision</h2>                <p>                LigoWave should become a leading <strong>wireless</strong> networking equipment developer, producer and distributor delivering <strong><a href="#" class="red">point-to-point</a></strong> and point-to-multipoint solutions in licensed and unlicensed bands.                </p>                <h2>Our values</h2>                <ul>                  <li>Commitment to outstanding customer support</li>                  <li>Devotion to quality, performance, innovation and cost-effectiveness from the start of development until the product reaches the end-user</li>                  <li>Continuous investment in knowledge enhancement and work effectiveness inside LigoWave company</li>                  <li>Promise to preserve the environment by the use of recycled and nature-friendly materials where possible during the production process</li>                </ul>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:21:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
