(206, 'Mission and vision', '                <h2>Our mission</h2>                <p>                We are committed to quality, innovation and performance and these values remain core during the development, production and distribution processes of LigoWave <strong><a href="#" class="red">wireless</a></strong> equipment. Today’s rapidly changing and quickly evolving <strong>wireless</strong> communication market requires swift reaction to the changes, dedication to quality and cost-effectiveness to deliver the desirable solutions to customers. LigoWave will continue to develop and produce premier line carrier grade <strong>wireless</strong> networking products and market them through its worldwide distribution network using the core values of the company.                </p>                <h2>Our vision</h2>                <p>                LigoWave should become a leading <strong>wireless</strong> networking equipment developer, producer and distributor delivering <strong><a href="#" class="red">point-to-point</a></strong> and point-to-multipoint solutions in licensed and unlicensed bands.                </p>                <h2>Our values</h2>                <ul>                  <li>Commitment to outstanding customer support</li>                  <li>Devotion to quality, performance, innovation and cost-effectiveness from the start of development until the product reaches the end-user</li>                  <li>Continuous investment in knowledge enhancement and work effectiveness inside LigoWave company</li>                  <li>Promise to preserve the environment by the use of recycled and nature-friendly materials where possible during the production process</li>                </ul>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:38:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
