ground-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">NOTE</span></span>: How to install SWEAP for Linux system please look at the&nbsp;<a href="http://deliberant.goodone.lt/media/files/SWEAP_QuickStart.pdf"><span style="color:#ef7f1a;"><span style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent;">Quick </span></span>start guide</a>.</p><div><br /></div><span style="line-height: 19px; "></span><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">Below you can see a video of how quick and easy SWEAP setup is (Windows version).</p><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/Azzx9HzJfDk" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="360" width="480"></iframe></div>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:38:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(228, 'LinkCalc', '<h2><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:13px;font-weight: normal; ">LigoWave‘s link calculator is a link planning tool available online at <a href="http://www.ligowave.com/linkcalc/" target="_blank">http://www.ligowave.com/linkcalc/</a>. The link calculator allows LigoPTP users to calculate link performance expectations taking into account geographical information, distance between the units, antenna height and gain, transmit power, and other factors in order to choose the most suitable product available from Ligowave‘s extensive product portfolio. In addition, custom calculations using other vendors’ equipment specs can be used, making the Ligowave link calculator the ultimate link planning tool. At the same time, this tool is offered free of charge, and users only need to register to get quick and easy access to this very helpful tool. Additionally, each user is able to save and create a database of links, download a PDF document that contains all the necessary information about the link, and publish a hyperlink online so that it could be shown to other people during the evaluation process.</span></h2><div><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:13px;font-weight: normal; ">The video below shows how to use LinkCalc.</span></div><div><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:13px;font-weight: normal; "><br /></span></div><iframe width="480" height="360" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/QriXwzD7snM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>', '<ul><li>Easy and quick planning;</li><li>Support of PTP (Point to Point) and PTMP (Point to Multipoint) mode;</li></ul><div><br /></div><p><a href="/uploads/PTPnPTMPnormal.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="/uploads/12-06-15/LCPTPPTMP.jpg" alt="" /></a></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Free online application and can be used with all wireless equipment;</li><li>Has integration with Google maps;<br /></li></ul><div><br /></div><div><img src="/uploads/12-06-15/maps.jpg" alt="" /><br /></div><div><br /></div><ul><li>Allows storing, downloading and publishing data about the links online.</li></ul><div><br /></div><div><img src="/uploads/12-06-15/store.jpg" alt="" /></div><ul><li>PDF results can even be used by installation teams!</li></ul>', 0, '2012-08-31 06:38:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(229, 'Reset tool', '<h2><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:13px;font-weight: normal; ">Reset Tool is written on Java and lets the users to restore the devices easily to their default configuration. No special commands are no more required. To use the reset tool, please upgrade your LigoPTP MiMo devices to software version 6.77. The new software version is available under the downloads section on the support tab together with the reset tool.</span></h2><p>  Click <a href="/media/files/reset-tool.noname.EN_.v1.1.42830.20120628.2113.jar">here</a> to download the reset tool. </p><br />Features<ul><li>Resets all LigoWave products</li><li>Discovers the devices automatically in the local subnet</li><li>Displays IP address, MAC address, firmware version</li><li>Performs reset by one click (requires power-cycle of the device)</li><li>Has an option to add the device manually</li><li>Works on Windows, Linux and MAC OS</li></ul><div><br /></div><div>Below you can see a movie on how to use the reset tool</div><div><br /><iframe width="480" height="360" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/xpqCJ7KbuNU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:38:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(230, 'LigoWave training programs', '<div style="width:50%;float:left">              <img src="/img/training-pa.jpg" alt="" />            </div>            <div style="width:50%;float:left">              <h2>Personal training courses</h2>              In addition to the Ligowave partner training courses, we are also offering custom training programs to partners that require a more in depth understanding of the capabilities of LigoWave products. This special training program will not only help with LigoWave equipment configuration, but will also teach you how to install and maintain our products, as well as other solution offerings custom tailored to your needs. Personal training sessions can either be held in our headquarters or our certified training staff can come and teach at your desired location. To inquire or learn more about our training courses, please email: <a href="mailto:training@ligowave.com">training@ligowave.com</a></div>              <div class="clr"></div>            <br />     <br />             <div style="width:50%;float:left;">              <h2>Online training</h2>              Beginning soon, LigoWave professional training courses will be held in our online partner portal. The courses will provide an excellent knowledge base for all LigoWave customers. Large telecom operators, smaller wireless internet service providers, and even our distributors and resellers that would like to train their sales and support staff are welcome to join our online video training . The partner portal will also contain information about our latest products and configuration specs. Additionally, there will be advice on deployment scenarios and how LigoWave products are able to save you money and time; two of the most valued business assets. All video training courses will be published in our partner zone where all registered partners are welcome to get the latest news from Ligowave: the innovators of the wireless industry.            </div>            <div style="width:50%;float:left">               <img src="/img/training-pb.jpg" alt="" align="right" />            </div>              <div class="clr"></div>  ', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:38:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(231, 'Steakwave', '<img src="/uploads/12-06-05/streakwave.jpg" alt="" /><h2>Distributor in USA and Canada</h2><p>Streakwave Wireless Inc, is a Global Value Added Distributor with distribution facilities in San Jose California and Salt Lake City Utah and is proud to offer a complete line of wireless solutions from top tier manufacturers. Streakwave offers equipment which utilizes both licensed and licensed free bands available for public use. Solutions include; Point to Point back hauls, Point to Multipoint systems and equipment for all other types of wireless and wired network applications. Primarily, Streakwave serves the Educational, Government, Corporate, Healthcare, Security and Consumer markets.</p><p>Streakwave prides itself on technical knowledge of the industry offering first tier technical support for most every product offered. Streakwave Wireless’ Sales Engineering / Account Management Team verbally assists our customers with all aspects of design, layout of networks, trouble shooting, site survey assistance and implementation. These attributes accompanied by unparalleled customer service proves Streakwave Wireless, Inc. is the leader among product equipment providers. Streakwave Wireless believes in outstanding customer service and we have built a quality team that will exceed the needs of our customers.</p><br /><a href="http://www.streakwave.com" target="_blank">www.streakwave.com</a>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:38:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(232, 'DoubleRadius', '<img src="/uploads/12-06-05/dradius.gif" alt="" /><h2>Distributor in USA and Canada</h2><p>DoubleRadius, Inc. was formed for the sole purpose of providing best of breed networking, consulting, designing, planning and financing solutions to the data communications community. We are focused on a wide range of customers including WISPs, municipalities, service providers, telecommunications companies, and utility companies.</p><p>Our full spectrum of resources combines a complete range of innovative products with the most experienced, knowledgeable professionals in the industry. We have partnered with the best manufacturers in the world to concentrate on WAN & LAN connectivity requirements including wireless, dial-up, DSL, routing, and switching.</p><p>Our solutions-oriented approach is driven by our desire to exceed the expectations of our customers.</p><br /><a href="http://www.doubleradius.com" target="_blank">www.doubleradius.com</a>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:38:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(233, 'Crossover ', '<img src="/uploads/12-06-05/crossover_logo_col_197_35.jpg" alt="" /><h2>Distributor in USA and Canada</h2><p>Crossover distribution Corp is a value-added distributor of wireless broadband, in-building cellular, telecom, VoIP, data networking and CATV technologies to the North American marketplace.  These technologies are purchased by telephone companies, internet service providers, cable TV operators and a national network of integrators, certified dealers, value-added resellers and contractors.They provide full service sales, engineering, technical support and logistics for their key vendor partners.  Crossover has a breakthrough, secure, password protected E-Commerce website that resellers can use to place and track orders, as well as review ordering history and pricing rates.  With Canadian offices located in Torontoand a US office located in Parsippany, New Jersey, they offer North American coverage and smooth order fulfillment.</p><br /><a href="http://www.crossoverdistribution.com/" target="_blank">www.crossoverdistribution.com/</a>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:38:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
