(244, 'X-Concepts', '<img src="/uploads/12-06-05/xconcepts_0.jpg" alt="" /><br /><p>X-Concepts assets are its business partners. We use the word partner specifically because the reason we exist is for their success which will eventually measure our success. We at X-Concepts will provide our partners with industry leading technologies and solutions. In X-Concepts we believe in strategic business relationships with customers and business partners to produce mutual benefits. We value those relationships and invest in their long term development. We aspire to be the best at everything we do, always striving to be the first choice for our customers and business partners. At X-Concepts we promote an environment of personal accountability that delivers consistent results against commitments.</p><br /> Xconcepts Asia Pacific <br />Office # 07-04<br />Burlington Square, Beside Sim Lin Centre<br />175 Bencoollen Street,<br />Singapore, 189649<br />+65-68845048 (T)<br /><br /><a href="mailto:sales@xconcepts-asiapacific.com">sales@xconcepts-asiapacific.com</a> <br /><br /> <a href="http://www.xconcepts-asiapacific.com" target="_blank">www.xconcepts-asiapacific.com</a>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:38:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(245, 'F1 Solutions', '<img src="/uploads/12-06-05/F1-logo.jpg" alt="" /><br /><p><strong>F1 Solutions Sdn Bhd</strong>, a wireless turnkey distribution company has its strong focus and presence within APAC particularly in Malaysia, Indonesia, Philippines and China aim to provide complete end-to-end wireless solution for its business partners and customers. Our wireless solutions cover the access, distribution and core layers of traditional TDM to IP Ethernet from Point-to-multipoint and Point-to-point radios in Sub 6Ghz and 7Ghz to 24Ghz.</p><p>  As a complete package, we offer to consult, built, operate and transfer services including distributed and centralized wireless infrastructure and service management platform for Government, Enterprise, Service Providers and Carriers. This includes automation of service provisioning, customers’ relationship management, billing and control irrespective of the sizes of subscribers’ base.</p><br /> Email:   <a href="mailto:jt@f1.net.my">jt@f1.net.my</a>         <br />Contact: Mr. Jim Teo       <br />              Mobile: +6012-2102717  <br />  <br />  <a href="http://www.f1dotcom.my" target="_blank">www.f1dotcom.my</a>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:38:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(246, 'Wireless Data Solutions', '<img src="/uploads/12-06-05/wds.gif" alt="" /><h2>Distributor for Australia and New Zealand</h2><p>Wireless Data Solutions is the premier Value Added Distributor for industrial / corporate grade wireless networking solutions in the Australian and New Zealand marketplace. WDS works with system integrators and resellers to deliver robust, scaleable, cost-effective solutions.</p><p>Through the use of point-to-point, point-to-multipoint, mobile data, SCADA, MESH, Wi-Fi and interconnect networking solutions, WDS delivers on its motto, &quot;Business Solutions in a Wireless World&quot;.</p><br /><a href="http://www.wirelessdata.com.au" target="_blank">www.wirelessdata.com.au</a>', '', 0, '2012-08-31 06:38:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
